!theme plain
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam nodesep 120
skinparam ranksep 100

' --- STYLING (Blue HIMS Theme) ---
skinparam rectangle {
 BackgroundColor #436FB6
 FontColor white
 BorderColor #2F528F
 FontSize 14
 Padding 15
}
skinparam usecase {
 BackgroundColor #436FB6
 FontColor white
 BorderColor #2F528F
 FontSize 14
 Padding 15
}
skinparam database {
 BackgroundColor #FFFFFF
 FontColor #436FB6
 BorderColor #436FB6
 FontSize 13
}
skinparam arrow {
 Color #2F528F
 FontColor #444444
 FontSize 11
 MessageAlign center
}

' --- EXTERNAL ENTITIES (Top Layer) ---
rectangle \"Passenger\" as Pass
rectangle \"Driver\" as Driver
rectangle \"Admin\" as Admin

' --- PROCESSES (Middle Layer) ---
usecase \"1.0\nManage User\nAuthentication\" as P1
usecase \"2.0\nProcess Live\nGPS Tracking\" as P2
usecase \"3.0\nRender Map\n& Estimates\" as P3
usecase \"4.0\nManage Fleet\n& Routes\" as P4

' --- DATA STORES (Bottom Layer) ---
database \"D1: Users\" as D1
database \"D2: Live Logs\" as D2
database \"D3: Routes/Buses\" as D3

' --- ALIGNMENT (The Invisible Grid) ---
Pass -[hidden]right- Driver
Driver -[hidden]right- Admin

P1 -[hidden]right- P2
P2 -[hidden]right- P3
P3 -[hidden]right- P4

' --- DATA FLOWS ---

' 1. AUTHENTICATION FLOWS (P1)
Pass --> P1 : \" Login Request\"
Driver --> P1 : \" Login Request\"
Admin --> P1 : \" Login Request\"
P1 --> D1 : \"Validate Credentials\"
D1 --> P1 : \"Auth Token\"
P1 --> Pass : \"Access Granted \"
P1 --> Driver : \"Access Granted \"

' 2. GPS TRACKING FLOWS (P2)
Driver --> P2 : \" Live Coordinates\n Start/Stop Trip\"
P2 --> D2 : \"Update Bus Location\"
P2 --> D3 : \"Check Bus Status\"

' 3. MAP VISUALIZATION FLOWS (P3)
Pass --> P3 : \" Search Query\"
D2 --> P3 : \"Fetch Real-Time Coords\"
D3 --> P3 : \"Fetch Route Paths\"
P3 --> Pass : \"Map View & ETA \"

' 4. ADMIN MANAGEMENT FLOWS (P4)
Admin --> P4 : \" Add/Edit Bus\n Modify Route\"
P4 --> D3 : \"Commit Changes\"
P4 --> D1 : \"Manage User Roles\"
D2 --> P4 : \"Fetch Active Fleet Data\"
P4 --> Admin : \"Dashboard View \"
